IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
  PROGRAM-ID. "scanf_demo".
DATA DIVISION.
  01 READ PICTURE IS 9999.
  01 A PICTURE IS 9.
PROCEDURE DIVISION.
MAIN.
  DISPLAY "Please enter a number of up to four digits".
  CALL scanf USING "%4d" AS PRIMITIVE BY REFERENCE READ AS PRIMITIVE.
  DISPLAY "You entered " READ.

  LOOP WHILE READ > 0
    DISPLAY "read is " READ
    ADD -1 TO READ
  END.

  DISPLAY "Finally, read is " READ.

  DISPLAY "DONE".

  END.